ActOld Age Security Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Agreement between the Government of Canada and the Government of Republic of Ecuador Concerning the Social Security
PrecisOrder authorizing (1) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT ON SOCIAL SECURITY BETWEEN CANADA AND THE REPUBLIC OF ECUADOR; or (2) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers, authorizing the individuals mentioned in the order, to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the Agreement.
